		    <li><img style="cursor: pointer;" title="Decrease font size" src="http://localhost/old_site/templates/jaolyra/images/user-decrease.gif" alt="Decrease font size" id="ja-tool-decrease" onclick="changeFontSize(-1); return false;" /></li>
